OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers and thunderstorms moving north
OL,7,Facross England and Wales through this
OL,8,Fevening and overnight. Otherwise dry
OL,9,Fwith clear spells, but low cloud
OL,10,Freturning in the northeast. A very
OL,11,Fwarm evening, but overall a cooler
OL,12,Fnight for many.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FMostly dry with sunny
OL,15,Fspells, but also a few showers and
OL,16,Fthunderstorms possibly breaking out
OL,17,Facross England & Wales later in the
OL,18,Fday. Warmer again for many.
